tartLine int) ([]transcript.Line, error) {\\n    lines, _, err := parseDroidTranscriptFromReader(bytes.NewReader(content), startLine)\\n    return lines, err\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### 2. Fix `calculateTokenUsage` for Droid\\n\\n**File:** `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_condensation.go` (lines 620-628)\\n\\nChange:\\n```go\\nif agentType == agent.AgentTypeFactoryAIDroid {\\n    lines, err := factoryaidroid.ParseDroidTranscriptFromBytes(data)\\n    if err != nil || len(lines) == 0 {\\n        return &agent.TokenUsage{}\\n    }\\n    if startOffset > 0 && startOffset < len(lines) {\\n        lines = lines[startOffset:]\\n    }\\n    return factoryaidroid.CalculateTokenUsage(lines)\\n}\\n```\\nTo:\\n```go\\nif agentType == agent.AgentTypeFactoryAIDroid {\\n    lines, err := factoryaidroid.ParseDroidTranscriptFromBytes(data, startOffset)\\n    if err != nil || len(lines) == 0 {\\n        return &agent.TokenUsage{}\\n    }\\n    return factoryaidroid.CalculateTokenUsage(lines)\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### 3. Update all other callers to pass `, 0`\\n\\nMechanical changes — add `, 0` as second arg:\\n\\n| File | Line | Context |\\n|------|------|---------|\\n| `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_condensation.go` | 553 | `extractUserPrompts` |\\n| `cmd/entire/cli/summarize/summarize.go` | 221 | `buildCondensedTranscriptFromDroid` |\\n| `cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/lifecycle.go` | 100 | `ExtractSummary` |\\n| `cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/factoryaidroid.go` | 145 | `ReadSession` |\\n| `cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/transcript_test.go` | lines 46, 123, 152, 186, 207, 1103 | Various tests |\\n\\n### 4. Add regression tests\\n\\n**a) In `cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/transcript_test.go`:**\\n\\nTest `ParseDroidTranscriptFromBytes` with non-message entries and a non-zero offset. Transcript with `session_start` + messages + `session_event` + messages. Verify that offset correctly skips raw lines and only returns messages after the offset.\\n\\n**b) In `cmd/enti